nodes.text: Je'daii Temple Master was a term which referred to a Force-sensitive who had exemplified as Je'daii Masters and demonstrated true understanding of the Force. Numbering around nine at a given time, the Temple Masters acted as stewards of the Great Temples of Tython and the leaders of the Je'daii Council of the Je'daii Order.

A rank within the Je'daii Order, Temple Masters had attained the highest position within the Order and represented the wisest minds on Tython. Making up the membership of the Je'daii Council, the Temple Masters were each appointed as the leader of one of the nine Great Temples of Tython.
